text: Yuliya Lobzhenidze is an archer from Ukraine. She was born on 23 August 1977. Lobzhenidze competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics,Yuliya LobzhenidzeYuliya LOBZHENIDZE == References == Category:Living people Category:1977 births Category:Ukrainian archers Category:Olympians for Ukraine
